data.description: Come to Northglen and see THIS ONE! 4 Bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms, an Office, Formal Dining, and TONS of extras! Walk in to the stunning entry way that features custom wood working and plenty of light pouring in from outside. You'll love the Living Area's focal point that holds a custom wood design as well as a smokeless biofuel fireplace. See the updated hard-surfaced flooring throughout all the rooms, as well as light neutral colors to give this home a modern feel. You'll find abundant counter space in the kitchen as well as breakfast seating and a Formal Dining area at the entry to the Kitchen. All the Kitchen appliances are newer as well as the HVAC System. There's tons of extra room and closet space in all bedrooms and a bonus office for you to work from or use as a second living area. Call now for a showing!
